quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  70,11,"Hi…ďe hollindiree. Bon…óo on yeloto sottorgol lette …óen nden √Īalnde, …ďi…ó…ďe makko …ďen"
  70,12,"e gennda makko, e neene gooto makko on"
  70,13,e gorol makko ngol moolayngol mo
  70,14,"e kala won…ďe ka leydi …ďen, fii no …óum da…óndira mo"
  70,15,"∆äum gasataa. Ngen [Yiite] ko uuyunge"
  70,16,…ďoltaynge guri hoore
  70,17,Hinge nodda on …óuurnii…óo o hucciti
  70,18,o moo…ďi (jawle) o mari e marirgel
  70,19,"Pellet, ne…ó…óo tagaama ko o …óen∆īotoo…óo"
  70,20,"si bone memii mo, o faaya"
  70,21,"si ko mo mo∆ī∆īere he…ďi mo, o salora"
  70,22,Si wanaa juuloo…ďe …ďen. @Corrected
  70,23,…ďen taw…ďe ko …ďe duumii…ďe e juulde ma…ď…ďe nden
  70,24,E …ďen taw…ďe hino ka jawle ma…ď…ďe haqqee anndaa…óo
  70,25,wonannde torotoo…óo e ha…óitii…ói
  70,26,e …ďen gom…óim…ďe √Īalaande njo…ďdi diina
  70,27,E …ďen taw…ďe ko …ďe hulu…ďe lette Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen
  70,28,"tawde pellet, lette Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen wanaa hoolnii…óe"
  70,29,E …ďen taw…ďe ko reenu…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin
  70,30,"si wanaa e rew…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa …ďen hor…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe …ďe jeyiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe, …óon on …ďe feletaake"
  70,31,"Kala non …óa…ď…ďu…óo [ka dakmitora] caggal …óum, haray ko …ďen woni jaggitu…ďe …ďen"
  70,32,E …ďen taw…ďe ko aynitu…ďe koolaaje e aadiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin
  70,33,E …ďen taw…ďe ko √Īii…ďu…ďe e seedeeji mun
  70,34,e …ďen taw…ďe ko reenoo…ďe e juulde ma…ď…ďe nden
  70,35,∆Āen …óon ko teddinoytee…ďe e Aljannaaji
  70,36,"E ko he…ďi yeddu…ďe …ďen takko maa…óa, hi…ďe he√Īora"
  70,37,"ka nano e ka √Īaamo, ko …ďe dentoy-dentoy"
  70,38,Hara gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe tam∆īinoto naatoygol Aljanna neemaaji
  70,39,∆äun wa…óataa ! Men tagiri…ďe ko …ďe anndi
